16:23.366 --> 16:25.267
Well, it's not your house.
It belongs to the bank.

16:25.268 --> 16:27.369
I know that 'cause I was
snooping through your files.

16:27.370 --> 16:29.438
Mindy, Trish and I
have a daughter together.

16:29.439 --> 16:31.106
She's always gonna be a part of my life.

16:31.107 --> 16:32.607
