18:07.437 --> 18:09.604
What? Oh, my God.

18:09.605 --> 18:12.908
Ben, do you understand my story?

18:12.909 --> 18:14.709
I think so.

18:14.710 --> 18:16.645
You just drank so much whiskey.

18:16.646 --> 18:18.413
Well, look at that.

18:18.414 --> 18:19.748
Ben, face it.

18:19.749 --> 18:22.384
It's like that old saying
